{"tid":865880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★標普警告：中國地方政府「瞞債」多　形勢似「鐵達尼」","createTime":"2018-10-17T12:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T12:27:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fae88ead7dc00c89f74ea49234ed45259e3dd9","tid":865880,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，根據評級機構標準普爾發表的報告顯示，中國地方政府可能「隱藏」了數以萬億美元計的債務，令中國債務佔國內生產總值(GDP)比例處於「警號」水平。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，中國地方政府在基建投資與獲得相關開發資金之間存在巨大差距，意味地方政府可能在「表外」(即官方監管以外)進行大量融資，金額達公開披露的數倍以上，估計介乎30萬億至40萬億元人民幣，即4.34萬億至5.78萬億美元。報告形容債務為「鐵達尼遇上冰山的信貸風險」，亦由此推算中國所有政府債務佔GDP比例於去年已達60%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181017/bkn-20181017172546778-1017_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181017%2Fbkn-20181017172546778-1017_00842_001.html&d=EuBWzc3B4ccnLZoBWH7bVNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9028cfc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181017/bkn-20181017172546778-1017_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fdca9791231b3ab240904c613678780d1b517edc","tid":865880,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf9500bbefd4cd524d0baa8126cbe4f24595a36","tid":865880,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/202244_0bcccf12bd11c8a50383b1f7b7d47001.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F202244_0bcccf12bd11c8a50383b1f7b7d47001.gif&h=96bea135&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6fed0536ac94dbe4978d956f7c2a101680486a1","tid":865880,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"國家主席月薪一萬<br />\n係香港有幾億港幣資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff610afe27c3d2dc24a3d81eb3bce7668dfbc912","tid":865880,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/202750_24b13a8321be530d1a8cee7120f9c99e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F202750_24b13a8321be530d1a8cee7120f9c99e.jpg&h=90d1ed03&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}